HEADWORD: chondrichthian
<hw>chondrichthian</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a fish in which the skeleton
may be calcified but not ossified; a cartilaginous fish.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cartilaginous fish.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

